Instructions:

1.Run "npm install" from Draw & Guess/server
2.Run "npm install" from Draw & Guess/my-draw-and-guess
3.Change "SERVER_IP" at Draw & Guess/my-draw-and-guessed/src/constants.js to your local SERVER_IP
4.On one process run node server.js from Draw & Guess/server
5.On second process run npm start from Draw & Guess/my-draw-and-guess


*All the website to be mobile responsive, i had a problem with connecting from my phone to server. all functionality tested on mobile.
*All required functionality is working.

